name: KetoCalculator
0:
”Alexa, Ask KetoCalc what is the exchange for cucumber?”
”Alexa, Ask KetoCalc what is the exchange for bacon?”
”Alexa, Ask KetoCalk the exchange for strawberry.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: keto calc
des: KetoCalc provides the grams per exchange of food items according to the program operated by the Children's Hospital of Philadelphia (CHOP). This skill is a convenience skill that is intended to provide the same information as the food catalog given by CHOP to families who are on the ketogenic diet. This app is not managed by or supported by CHOP and all exchange values should be verified before use.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
